@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pprqke(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.94 * v2 + 0.68)) + v1)
    tmp = wp.exp(0.98)
    v0 = v0
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v0 + 0.84 / v0 + 0.63)))
    v0 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.41 - v0 + 0.11)) - v0)
    v1 = wp.abs(((v0 + 0.12 + v0 + 0.45) - wp.abs(tmp + 0.48)))
    v0 = (0.67 * ((tmp + 0.22 / tmp + 0.73) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.52)))
    data[tid] = v0
